songs.title: Interlude (Erick Rush)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse: Erick Rush]

Free world music baby!
It's a global thing, you already know what's good
But right now you guys just stepped into Price City
In the city where everything has a price
Sometimes you gotta drop something priceless on 'em
Ain't that right?
And this time the little homie's loose
He's off the chains
He's off the muzzle
The cage is opened, the beast is unleashed!
Nasty C, come out and feast on these niggas man
The motherfucking prince dawg
Y'all niggas think y'all rapping out there?
Y'all niggas thinking y'all really spitting out there?
Okay!
Just press play
Press play to the song after that
Go to the next song after that
Go through the next song after that
Then get back at me nigga
Price city nigga, you already know what's good
Free world music
Erick Rush
Southside still holding
